        <abstract>
            <p>Expresses pleasure at signs of CD’s recovery.</p> 
<p>HWB’s work on the identification of species of the genus <hi rend="italic">Colobthea</hi>; relates the large number of modifications that occur in the sexual organs of closely allied species. Does not doubt that this contributes greatly to multiplication of species in nature.</p> 
        </abstract>
